Go for the whole square pie.  Grab a seat and don't you dare leave until every slice is gone.   The cheese is under the sauce!  My guy was skeptical but once he took a bite, I think he almost proposed.   Bathroom could use some work ( totally gross) but you get to watch how the pizza is made while you do the pee pee dance  standing on line.  Lets hope the cooks use a better bathroom.
